Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.40,0:00:38.11,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,800)\pos(600,302)}『遺失的未來』
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.98,0:00:39.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個給你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.37,0:00:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.52,0:00:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  你又熬夜看望遠鏡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:47.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.11,0:00:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚啊  小時候的奏出現在夢裡了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:00:55.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭著問我「怎樣才能抓到星星呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:00:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時候的奏真是可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.44,0:01:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都哭著說想要星星了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.38,0:01:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.16,0:01:09.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.61,0:01:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.22,0:01:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來擦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.27,0:01:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,行了你快吃早飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.71,0:01:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧奏  佳織都變可靠了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.25,0:01:26.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽你快去重新倒一杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:27.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.59,0:01:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  你也別傻站著了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  佐佐木同學怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意中人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:47.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是幫我問問啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.46,0:01:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是受朋友所託啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.82,0:01:51.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你自己去問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.13,0:01:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不不  我要去問的話她肯定會誤會的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們是從小就在一起了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:01:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.31,0:02:00.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  要是問了這問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.33,0:02:04.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都得活在微妙的氛圍當中了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.57,0:02:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是啊  這個月她都拒絕三個人了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.42,0:02:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定會在意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.55,0:02:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…一般來說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說你們都住在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:14.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道不會隨口談起類似的問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.01,0:02:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佐佐木同學就跟你在同一屋簷下洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且是每天每天每天每天…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.64,0:02:25.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古典文學的作業是今天交？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.89,0:02:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了  快給我抄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得幫我把佐佐木同學的入浴場景拍下來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.20,0:02:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:33.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開玩笑的開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.67,0:02:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還什麼都沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會讓你抄作業的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.68,0:02:45.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是給你吃草莓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:48.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不會被草莓收買的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.72,0:02:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感覺自己今天會被抽中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:54.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你總是這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.02,0:02:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次會去La Mer買蛋糕給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:02:59.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.39,0:03:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要草莓蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:09.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多謝  先撤了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉  敗給蛋糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.19,0:03:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是蛋糕嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了  是蛋糕蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  我能拿一個炸雞塊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表示下友誼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果斷拒絕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey  奏  現在不是吃便當的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.83,0:03:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們的會長大人貌似在幹一件exciting的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許需要幫手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.31,0:03:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等KENNY  我還沒吃完飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.94,0:03:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了  佳織也一起Let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要碰我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.74,0:03:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制伏她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說叫你們…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.69,0:04:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.79,0:04:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到不用我們出場了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該說很遺憾我們來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.13,0:04:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,華宮學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐原來你在啊  什麼時候來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…一開始就在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.61,0:04:19.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就麻煩您阻止下她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.58,0:04:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  大家都來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.71,0:04:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不來嗎你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.46,0:04:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.82,0:04:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問我在幹什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:30.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:35.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在調停？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是疑問句啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這些人扭打在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就想著要勸勸來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:44.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是故意要弄成這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是話劇部的這些傢伙先襲擊過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.11,0:04:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你們把我們的招牌給弄壞的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.51,0:04:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼證據嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.79,0:04:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種東西…沒有是沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.19,0:04:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但除了你們還會有誰幹出這種事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:02.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說啥？找碴是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是先爽快地向對方道歉比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.03,0:05:16.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…這個不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}果然是你們做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼有照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:24.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個你們就不用知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.96,0:05:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:28.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.33,0:05:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學生會長還有副會長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.32,0:05:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:35.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後就拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:36.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.07,0:05:37.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.38,0:05:40.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我們看好你們天文學會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是有事要拜託你們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.35,0:05:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.99,0:05:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是你來回答啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.92,0:05:45.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化節期間就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他那邊也當沒聽到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.03,0:05:51.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就簡單說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.81,0:05:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可理喻
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.46,0:05:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,維護治安算啥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.51,0:05:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是天文學會該幹的事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是風紀委員幹的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.89,0:06:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是想把麻煩的事情推給我們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.08,0:06:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你  愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.67,0:06:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.24,0:06:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要幹太危險的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.43,0:06:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會長也說要盡可能採取和平手段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是嘴上說說而已啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.24,0:06:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正會長肯定是想看好戲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我們的那一刻起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.15,0:06:19.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就注定不可能會和平啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.97,0:06:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}愛理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:24.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.60,0:06:26.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}我會控制自己的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.56,0:06:27.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}不要把我捲進去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.29,0:06:28.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個到底是什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.25,0:06:35.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的研究所那邊已經幫忙調查過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.63,0:06:37.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是這樣裝神秘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.26,0:06:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  影研的照片也是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要調查那種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是華宮會給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.47,0:06:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:47.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.84,0:06:50.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,華宮會是學姐的粉絲會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  也就是一群對我言聽計從的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:06:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是可以破例讓奏和KENNY入會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.69,0:07:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}太好了  請我喝三杯果汁哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.22,0:07:04.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}Oh My~
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:08.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}KENNY可以讓讓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.99,0:07:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來  今年的文化節上天文學會要幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望能創造一份美好的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.71,0:07:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我來說是高中最後的文化節了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文化節  啊  我也想叫上Jennifer
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.79,0:07:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My sweet heart
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.61,0:07:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wanna hold you tight
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我看看照片嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.25,0:07:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.49,0:07:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎樣都好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就交給你們決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏你完全沒幹勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.83,0:07:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實在的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.99,0:07:38.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起學校活動我覺得看星星比較有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種東西的魅力在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,星星這種存在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.84,0:07:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算現在是在發著光的但也可能其實已經不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:49.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一想到這一瞬間看到的星星或許再也看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.83,0:07:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多讓人興奮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有個好主意  大家一起去看星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.37,0:07:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會給你們進行詳細解說的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:07:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無所謂啦  反正很閒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那坐我家的車去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:05.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  奏  要不要做個天象儀？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.73,0:08:12.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小學的時候有試做過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在桌子上就能看的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.92,0:08:16.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好懷念啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在能做出更棒的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黏一個大圓頂  做出滿天的星星嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:27.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會蠻辛苦的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家齊心協力的話一定能做成的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.71,0:08:32.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是無所謂的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然是會幫你的  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  讓我們轟轟烈烈地給華宮學姐送終吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:41.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這說法太不吉利了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:49.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家裡有投影機和星座圖可以用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.18,0:08:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圓頂的材料和尺寸要怎麼辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.36,0:08:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是聽不太懂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.77,0:08:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但現在的奏很Happy吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:09:02.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織真是懂得如何讓奏高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.50,0:09:07.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天說那段子不膩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都說了佳織只是青梅竹馬而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.21,0:09:16.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛理  圓頂能做多大？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望能盡量大些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:19.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.49,0:09:22.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正要做不如搞個大的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這教室的空間都用上的那種
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幹勁來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.60,0:09:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛理  預算能用多少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.41,0:09:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是需要跟學生會申請的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:35.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明剛才完全沒有幹勁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.70,0:09:37.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真髒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛剛是想咬我的腳對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.58,0:09:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不能穿條性感點的內褲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.59,0:09:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在看什麼啊  這個…這個…色狼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.79,0:09:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.96,0:09:56.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  有東西要買
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.21,0:10:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  那麼明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh  傷害大和撫子的行為讓人不敢苟同哦  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:09.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.83,0:10:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快追過去啊  真不懂體貼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:20.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在生什麼氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.75,0:10:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:34.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.77,0:10:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  要吃蛋糕嗎蛋糕
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好  佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛理  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:06.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天是一個人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們兩人好好談談吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.76,0:11:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.22,0:11:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛理你對奏…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他喜歡你哦  一定是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:22.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是太笨了不會表達而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織你真是可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:44.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:47.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,柔道部跟空手道部的爭執
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都按耐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偏偏來這麼麻煩的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.12,0:11:54.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空有柔道部這名號實際都是些流氓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真讓人心跳加速啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:58.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織你還是回活動室比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.30,0:11:59.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:02.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用不著你擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別小瞧人啊你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信不信我幹掉你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我放手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.13,0:12:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了  到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.68,0:12:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天文學會？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.85,0:12:17.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  學姐你什麼時候來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.49,0:12:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從一開始就在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.79,0:12:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說是我們社團的一年級生撞到了他們的二年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.06,0:12:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後他們就跑過來找麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:30.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉  這事情太蠢了我都無言了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們就不覺得丟人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:34.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,空手道部是正經社團不會動手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是你們就來找事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別給我來這套
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:43.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊那位佐佐木佳織還不是用飯局和便當收買了空手道部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.95,0:12:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓人家把文化節上的表演時間給縮減了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丟人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.92,0:12:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是通過正當手段協商來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.38,0:12:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收買的人就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.74,0:12:52.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:56.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷靜一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.12,0:12:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是為了表示感謝才給他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.28,0:13:00.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你撤回收買這個說法！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.20,0:13:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.83,0:13:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.27,0:13:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混帳找死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.42,0:13:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這小…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:22.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好沒什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.00,0:13:28.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可不許再亂來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.81,0:13:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正義感過剩強出頭可是很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事  你先回去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底要生氣到什麼時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:44.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是時候消消氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:50.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.16,0:13:53.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏你太耍賴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總是耍賴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說你們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算學習再好體育再棒也不能老這樣胡來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:07.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.64,0:14:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起啦呢  這樣的你真的有在反省嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.92,0:14:12.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說長船
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別一副得意的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.25,0:14:16.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是在表揚你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管怎麼樣  你們都要做一定的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.57,0:14:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.78,0:14:21.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了  華宮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.86,0:14:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師  我有話想對您說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.25,0:14:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  感覺好像在看什麼不該看的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.79,0:14:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.54,0:14:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這次就這樣原諒你們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.97,0:14:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下不為例哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那張紅通通的Face是搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:49.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟你說也行  不過不是什麼有趣的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.30,0:14:58.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然在食堂吃飯  真稀奇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  今天詩織阿姨大大的睡過了頭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.02,0:15:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才跑來食堂而不是吃便當啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.21,0:15:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  話說是今天要去看星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.48,0:15:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對對  你還記得啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.60,0:15:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好  佳織的樣子怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.78,0:15:15.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是老樣子  不知在生什麼氣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.31,0:15:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  你可要多替佳織想想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.60,0:15:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊  搞得這麼嚴肅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.10,0:15:26.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然  我也沒辦法再邁出腳步了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.09,0:15:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天天氣也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該能清楚地看到星星吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.03,0:15:42.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還是不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.09,0:15:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們大家玩得開心點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.17,0:15:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織你不在可就不能算作「大家」了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.91,0:15:52.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說  我是想和你一起去看的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我先去活動室了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  那裡的四顆星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.88,0:16:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是秋季四邊形
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.66,0:16:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,組成了飛馬座的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.68,0:16:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  風好舒服  好想睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.18,0:16:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  完全沒在聽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真希望我們的天象儀也能像這一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.23,0:16:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.66,0:16:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  你是叫我搞一個出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  諾貝爾獎  億萬富翁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,願Jennifer不會被別的男人搶走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還是祈願一下胸部的成長吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.55,0:16:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  住腳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}我錯了  我錯了好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.12,0:16:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  你沒有願望嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.09,0:16:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話我希望現在能有誰來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.20,0:16:53.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.26,0:16:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.36,0:16:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.40,0:16:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:16:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要和平就好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.21,0:17:00.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.82,0:17:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可別浪費這麼浪漫的氛圍哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.55,0:17:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴巴有些渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.61,0:17:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想喝點熱的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.10,0:17:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來的時候我好像看到有自動販賣機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喝咖啡就可以了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.27,0:17:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織喝紅茶可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那個  我還…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.70,0:17:20.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們馬上會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.65,0:17:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  那就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.59,0:17:32.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏還真是讓人操心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.39,0:17:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏也到了該秋後算錢的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是算帳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.03,0:17:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛理你就甘願這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.73,0:17:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我又沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.82,0:17:44.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難受的時候就該吃點甜的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.13,0:17:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糖  糖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.52,0:17:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好孩子  好孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.49,0:17:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh  又是流星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.16,0:17:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望文化節能熱熱鬧鬧的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.17,0:18:04.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  會不會就這樣飄起來然後被星空吸走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.09,0:18:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在說胡話了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終於又看到你不生氣的臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.10,0:18:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.30,0:18:19.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我像小孩子一樣的鬧彆扭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.86,0:18:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要說聲對不起  雖然還不太明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流星結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.18,0:18:37.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  你們要出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:43.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  到樓上去看一下剩餘的物資
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.63,0:18:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:45.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  和KENNY兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凪沙學姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.60,0:18:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去學生會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天順利吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.78,0:18:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  她已經不生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.76,0:19:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下記得要告訴我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.58,0:19:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼說才能讓她這麼春心蕩漾的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.42,0:19:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就說了句「雖然還不太明白但我也要說聲對不起」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.24,0:19:08.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.05,0:19:09.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:10.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這一句？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.67,0:19:11.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後佳織心情就變得這麼好了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:15.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對你太失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.89,0:19:28.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  疼  啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.66,0:19:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.09,0:19:32.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從心底對你失望了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.75,0:19:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活動室裡的茶葉已經沒了  我想去買一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶葉店很早就會關門的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.48,0:19:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:51.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:56.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.24,0:19:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.93,0:20:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是家人或兄妹的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.96,0:20:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是另一種的  喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.05,0:20:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃  那個  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不對  怎麼了啊  突然這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.62,0:20:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經不想再當青梅竹馬了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才會生你的氣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.73,0:20:27.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.42,0:20:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想知道你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  也很重視佳織你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.63,0:20:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:40.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也會想…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.01,0:20:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是能一直和你在一起就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.40,0:20:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.57,0:20:58.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏你又耍賴了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.90,0:21:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用現在  但一定要對我有交代哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.55,0:21:05.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就待會兒見
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:12.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.94,0:22:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會蠻辛苦的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.95,0:22:19.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家齊心協力的話一定能做成的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.46,0:22:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是無所謂的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我當然是會幫你的  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.94,0:22:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  讓我們轟轟烈烈地給華宮學姐送終吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.86,0:22:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這說法太不吉利了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.47,0:22:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.40,0:22:37.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Earthquake？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.51,0:22:40.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  這和地震的聲音不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.54,0:22:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是去看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.13,0:22:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.15,0:22:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就留在這裡看門了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.44,0:22:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  那就分頭調查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.91,0:22:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  慘不忍睹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.23,0:23:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道是哪個倒霉蛋得來打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.13,0:23:05.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人體模型？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:14.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.73,0:23:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佳織…
